{"tid":1122650,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"TU要點先靚?","createTime":"2019-04-24T05:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T08:13:11.000Z","uid":92110,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c01c8fd31b72702ab3cf64f062051dbb4c895080","tid":1122650,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"好似話開多啲卡，減少借貸比率<br />\n準時還錢清卡數etc.<br />\n<br />\n我時不時借啲錢，借完拿拿林還，比起我冇借過，邊個option TU靚D?"},{"pid":"b19c29830eba8c54d000c21226f9e0abd037cfa1","tid":1122650,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c01c8fd31b72702ab3cf64f062051dbb4c895080","tid":1122650,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"好似話開多啲卡，減少借貸比率<br />\n準時還錢清卡數etc.<br />\n<br />\n我時不時借啲錢，借完拿拿林還，比起我冇借過，邊個option TU靚D?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"後者, 有借貸紀錄參考"},{"pid":"471cd8549a4c3ed202b079e808e4ff2a62fed809","tid":1122650,"uid":25822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c01c8fd31b72702ab3cf64f062051dbb4c895080","tid":1122650,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"好似話開多啲卡，減少借貸比率<br />\n準時還錢清卡數etc.<br />\n<br />\n我時不時借啲錢，借完拿拿林還，比起我冇借過，邊個option TU靚D?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"唔知關唔關事<br />\n<br />\n兩年前TU攞A，跟住屎忽痕開多張雙幣信用卡，點知後尾check TU發覺跌左一截，我又冇拖卡數，我估計每開一張卡銀行就check你一次TU，所以你所講開多d卡有保留"},{"pid":"301450ea9b0c5a033b773b7968f22f9bdc6576e7","tid":1122650,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"本身己經有係A或者B就好難升架啦, 正正常常用返一早開左既信用卡, <br />\n個個月找晒卡數慢慢就會升<br />\n<br />\n開卡同去銀行/財仔借錢係會扣分架, 雖然準時還會慢慢升返<br />\n最好係用返本身既卡, 個個月生活洗費碌卡, 再準時還, 咁就可以唔扣分既情況下加分"},{"pid":"e6c80bc8dfa33762fbf23ddbd893c0688f2c86d1","tid":1122650,"uid":222868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"遲找卡數會仆街<br />\n<br />\n即使是遲清還卡數僅一日都會影響信貸評級。就算立即清還仍會在信貸紀錄留下污點，一留就是5年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.transunion.hk/zh/blog/credit-score/6-ways-to-improve-tu-credit-score\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transunion.hk%2Fzh%2Fblog%2Fcredit-score%2F6-ways-to-improve-tu-credit-score&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=eac679f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.transunion.hk/zh/blog/credit-score/6-ways-to-improve-tu-credit-score</a>"},{"pid":"d02aa805124caaad76889c0caa9756f618ac5a0b","tid":1122650,"uid":222868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"適當地有借有還，信貸記錄絕對會比白紙一張更優勝。<br />\n<br />\n另外，只用一張信用卡走天下或許易於管理，但未必是提升信貸評分的最佳辦法。假如你擁有一張信用額50,000元的信用卡，碌卡40,000元，信貸使用度是80%。但如果如你手持兩張信用額相同的卡，額度就倍增至10萬元，消費40,000元的信貸使用度就會下降至40%，這樣可避免因信貸使用度過高而對信貸評級造成負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/TU-improve-credit-score-credit-card\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planto.hk%2Fzh%2Fblog%2FTU-improve-credit-score-credit-card&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a29fdfe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/TU-improve-credit-score-credit-card</a>"},{"pid":"c6a74130b83cbbf5b60748df18cec376caf878a8","tid":1122650,"uid":236653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"洗鬼理咩 <br />\n掉到落F一樣開到卡借到錢做到按揭<br />\n同A一樣息"},{"pid":"50d516aeec941eff5c0a1b1c2a23b11a1e1ce3fd","tid":1122650,"uid":23043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"Interesting.."}]}